#. ~ Description for South Gate Station
#: .\subway_factions.json
msgid ""
"South Gate is an autonomous community and not a member of United Stations, "
"but could become its first member in south Underrail. It is the most "
"powerful station in the entire south Lower Underrail."
msgstr ""

#: .\subway_factions.json
msgid "Underrail Malcontents"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for Underrail Malcontents
#: .\subway_factions.json
msgid ""
"Whether they're driven by wanderlust, greed or just a savage bloodlust, the "
"underrail has always generated an underclass of degenerate criminals. These "
"vandals prey upon the weak, and are generally without redemption."
msgstr ""

#: .\subway_factions.json
msgid "Red Line"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for Red Line
#: .\subway_factions.json
msgid ""
"With one of the largest populations in the Underrail, an unparalleled "
"capacity for mass conscription, and a number of stations and metres of track"
" surpassed only by South Gate Station, the Red Line is one of the most "
"formidable factions in the cataclysm world."
msgstr ""

#: .\subway_factions.json
msgid "4th Reich"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for 4th Reich
#: .\subway_factions.json
msgid ""
"The Nazis are a fascist faction in the Metro centred around several stations"
" which they dub The Reich. However, they maintain numerous outposts and a "
"military presence in several outlying stations, possibly in an attempt at "
"expansion since the Nazis are an imperialist faction."
msgstr ""

