#: .\Metro\NPCs\Talk_metro_redciv.json
msgid ""
"Things can get pretty rough at times. I don't know what's worse, the "
"nosalises that threaten us outside the metro, or the commissars breathing "
"down our necks. I guess it's better than being dead, though."
msgstr ""

