"instead of horns though, they have massive brains that they use to power "
"their psionic abilities. Azuridae are so called due to the azure hue on "
"their carapace. Their psionic powers have granted them nicknames such as psi"
" beetle and psi bug by residents of the Underrail."
msgstr ""

