msgid ""
"Crawlers live in dark places, both ruins and caves and haunt the nightmares "
"of Underrail and metro denizens alike. They look like pony-sized black "
"scorpions. Beware if you find one, for the few moments of your life left to "
"you might be brief."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid "nosalis"
msgid_plural "nosaliss"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nosalis'}
#: .\UnderRail\sgs_mobs.json
msgid ""
"Nosalises are the standard enemy of the metro. They are fierce predators, "
"extremely territorial, and can easily overwhelm fortified positions in large"
" numbers. Common between all types however, is a bipedal and humanoid shape "
"with two arms and legs, arched spines, and large round heads that "
"prominently display big noses, gaping jaws, and huge teeth. Their nests are "
"seemingly everywhere in the metro, but the creatures are less frequently "
"seen on the surface."
msgstr ""

