#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "What is it like being a cook in this station?"
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "Could I get any food?"
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"I truly love my job around here. Sure the food might be pretty basic: a few "
"selections of cavehopper meat and farmed potatoes, but it never gets old "
"seeing the look on people's faces when they eat this slop."
msgstr ""

#. 
#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve a copy of Cooking on a
#. Budget.'}'
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "Retrieve a copy of Cooking on a Budget."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"I'll let you in on a little secret, well perhaps it's not very little. I'm "
"not a very good cook and I think people are starting to become aware of "
"that, could you help me out by finding me a cookbook, it would be a great "
"help."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Help me find a copy of the book 'Cooking on a Budget'. I'm not a very good "
"cook, and I could use the knowledge contained within that text."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Thanks for accepting my offer."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Ouch, I guess people are gonna have to get used to cave hopper burgers for a"
" long while."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Libraries, Schools and Homes might have a cookbook or two, see what you can "
"find."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "Have you found what I requested yet?"
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid "Great work, I'll become a master chef in no time."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_gun_merchant.json
msgid "That's odd, I don't really know what to say."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_cook.json
msgid ""
"Well, you did what you could. It's just that food will be as bland as ever."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "South Gate Doctor"
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "What is it like being a doctor in this station?"
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"It's actually pretty easy, all things considered. Most of the time people "
"come back with little more than a few cave hopper scratches. Watch out for "
"nighstalkers though, they can be pretty nasty."
msgstr ""

#. 
#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Retrieve a syringe of adrenaline.'}'
#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Retrieve a syringe of adrenaline."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Look, I'm a bit busy here, but I think you could help me out here. I fear "
"that more skirmishes with other stations are on the horizon, and its "
"imperative that we prepare for any eventuality. Would you be willing to get "
"me an adrenaline syringe?"
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Would you be willing to get me an adrenaline syringe? I think the troops out"
" in the Underrail would greatly appreciate it."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "That's unfortunate."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Look for doctor's officers and hospitals on the surface, you'll probably "
"find some there."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid "Great work, this adrenaline will be useful."
msgstr ""

#: .\UnderRail\NPCs\sgs_doctor.json
msgid ""
"Well, you did what you could. but it's unfortunate that we'll be lacking "
"adrenaline."
msgstr ""

